                  <summary change="#ai-catalogue">
                     <p>رساله اخلاقيه</p>
                     <p>A Persian manual of ethics for the instruction of children by the same
                        author, Aqá-yi-Mutarjim Ibn Muhammad Mahdi of Tabriz.</p>
                     <p>Begins:</p>
                     <p>الحمد لله الملك المنّان خلق الانسان علمه البيان ... امّا بعد بر روی حقیقت نمای صاحبان تمیز و تمكين ... مخفی و پوشیده نیست</p>
                     <p>Pp. 136 of 21,8 x 17,3 c. and 13 ll. Nim-shikasta. Transcribed at Qum, in
                        the course of a week, during the month of Jumádà 1, 1295/May, 1878, by Mahdi
                        ibn Aqa Shaykh Hasan, called Shaykh Ustad-i-Qummi. From the library of Mr C.
                        Lyne.</p>
                  </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Y_8-item1">
